<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Problema com pagamento</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f4f5;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f4f4f5;padding:40px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#dc2626;padding:30px;text-align:center;">
              <h1 style="color:#ffffff;margin:0;font-size:24px;">Valya</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 30px;">
              <h2 style="color:#1a1a2e;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:20px;">Ola, <%= name %></h2>
              <p style="color:#52525b;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;">
                Identificamos um <strong>problema com a renovacao da sua assinatura</strong> com vencimento em <strong><%= dueDate %></strong>.
              </p>
              <div style="background-color:#fef2f2;border-left:4px solid #dc2626;padding:16px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin:0 0 24px;">
                <p style="color:#991b1b;font-size:15px;margin:0;">O pagamento nao foi processado. Verifique seus dados de pagamento para evitar a interrupcao do servico.</p>
              </div>
              <div style="text-align:center;margin:0 0 24px;">
                <a href="<%= supportUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;background-color:#dc2626;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;">Atualizar dados de pagamento</a>
              </div>
              <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Se voce ja regularizou o pagamento, desconsidere este e-mail.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#f4f4f5;padding:20px 30px;text-align:center;">
              <p style="color:#a1a1aa;font-size:12px;margin:0;">&copy; <%= year %> Valya. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
